The Syndicate is a loosely organized criminal organization of various walks of life, ranging everywhere from anti-capitalists, to anarchists, to private military companies, or even to people who had no other choice but to join. Everyone has their own reasons for joining but the main thing uniting most of the willing members of the Syndicate is a hatred for mega corporations. Hence their main adversary being [[Lore:NanoTrasen | NanoTrasen]].

== Structure ==

Due to the Syndicate's vast but disorderly nature there is no solid central structure for their organization, they instead operate more in localized Syndicate cells who all run themselves in different manners. Generally, most Syndicate activity is covert so the grand majority of cells don't need to be large and don't need outward communication.

Now, while most operations are covert, there is still the [[Lore:Gorlex Marauders | Gorlex Marauders]]. A notable branch of the Syndicate that specializes in overt action, terrorism, and military combat. They have established several long standing outposts and a group of commanders who lead a few small space fleets and several military units.

== History ==

Sometime after the Sol government's several dealings with NT, the Syndicate was formed by a few disgruntled NT employees in conjunction with a small criminal organization who opposed NT's principles and were looking to capitalize on a low security company while spreading their message. The Syndicate would operate as covertly as possible for their initial operations, it mostly consisted of small thefts that'd go unnoticed. The need for making an impact grew though and they slowly ramped up their aggressions till eventually they were interdicting supply transports and causing NT noticeable losses. The issue for the Syndicate is that NT started snapping back with new security measures and worst of all they were working.

The Syndicate needed to do something big. (WIP)